lyrics:
[verse]
There once was a monkey so jolly and fun
She danced and she sang in the bright morning sun
Her name was Makaka, oh how she loved to play
Swinging and jumping throughout the whole day

[chorus]
Hey there Makaka, let's join in the groove
Sing and dance together, move, move, move
La la la la, la la la la
With our friend Makaka, we'll have a blast
